Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: National miners' strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0409pgq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Dec 1977
Miners strike called as energy plans top national agenda. Middle East talks face crisis over securing oil supplies. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less